{"tid":1642791,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】據報中美副代表級別貿談無進展 道期曾挫逾300點","createTime":"2019-10-10T00:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T01:00:52.000Z","uid":66271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"564c5e142b5e81925038dbc9dbc85a9e53abc108","tid":1642791,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:52:36.000Z","msg":"中美舉行新一輪高級別貿易談判在即，報道指中美在副代表級別的貿易談判中沒有進展，道期下挫，曾跌逾300點。<br />\n<br />\n道期最新報26040點，跌265點或1%。至於有「黑期」之稱的新加坡HS50指數則跌約200點。<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》引述兩位不具名知情人士報道稱，中美在副代表級別的貿易談判中沒有取得任何進展。中國拒絕解決強制技術轉讓問題，而在勸說美國暫停上調關稅上未能取得進展。副代表級別談判重點在農產品採購和智慧財產權保護，談判亦避開國家補貼問題。"},{"pid":"a82e3e0f191a276f13ea4dd9020d70ed54e48865","tid":1642791,"uid":120913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:54:35.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我層樓會凍過水可能負資產但我咁撚愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac94c18c1520c3325a33c9561977e3f5574eceb5","tid":1642791,"uid":167340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:55:48.000Z","msg":"Old news?<br />\n升181 wo"},{"pid":"024383663862ed334f4a2585f003736d047caae9","tid":1642791,"uid":24833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac94c18c1520c3325a33c9561977e3f5574eceb5","tid":1642791,"uid":167340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:55:48.000Z","msg":"Old news?<br />\n升181 wo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T0